snippet.title: Eternights - Release Date Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/eternights/

Save your date. Save THE date. Save the world. Eternights is coming to PS5 & PS4 September 21st 2023. Pre-order available now: store.playstation.com/concept/10004814

Eternights is a dating action game, blending a love story with adrenaline-driven combat as you make the most out of life during the apocalypse. Scavenge for supplies, explore dungeons... and go on dates!

#ps5 & #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
